{"tid":2422543,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Bloodborne製作人宣佈離職SIE Japan Studio","createTime":"2021-02-25T09:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T09:32:49.000Z","uid":384047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03f97bd55624e5e9a766bb89d1ae84bd5e83fe11","tid":2422543,"uid":384047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/giwamasa/status/1364776713280913412?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgiwamasa%2Fstatus%2F1364776713280913412%3Fs%3D19&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=97e2e5fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgiwamasa%2Fstatus%2F1364776713280913412%3Fs%3D19&h=92937a2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/giwamasa/status/1364776713280913412?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還在等待《血源詛咒》更多續作？你可能需要先知道這件事情。《血源詛咒》製作人山際真晃即將於 2 月底離開索尼互動娛樂日本工作室（SIE Japan Studio）。<br />\n<br />\n山際真晃今（25）日在個人 Twitter 帳號，告知自己即將在 2 月底自索尼離職，未來會繼續努力從事遊戲開發。<br />\n<br />\n2001 年山際真晃加入索尼，曾參與 PS3《東京叢林》（Tokyo Jundle）、PS4《血源詛咒》，以及 PS VR《失根D&eacute;racin&eacute;》等作品，並曾於 2015 年因著宣傳《血源詛咒》造訪台北國際電玩展。<br />\n<br />\n附帶一提，過去同樣在 Japan Studio 參與《血源詛咒》的製作人鳥山晃之，早一步在 2020 年 12 月離開索尼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46820/bloodborne-producer-masaaki-yamagiwa-leaves-sony-japan-studio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F46820%2Fbloodborne-producer-masaaki-yamagiwa-leaves-sony-japan-studio&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFbQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=23b366c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46820/bloodborne-producer-masaaki-yamagiwa-leaves-sony-japan-studio</a><br />\n<br />\n畢幫2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b67814e61da124dac8540f2259f13d923b35271","tid":2422543,"uid":3405,"like":0,"